song.title: Dig Deep
song.info:
dig deep 303 blowout remix : chuck biscuits / mono
This started off as an ambient groove and then through some inspiration provided to me via OLN's "orporto deep cuts" on Tribal, it transformed into a deep house groove, only to be supplmeneted with the cutting edge of the 303 bassline in this remix. hope you're playing this on a big system, because the doubled kick is large :)
Greets go out to: injekted for the oldskool phat US beats
